---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Home | Hello Subconscious"
  description="A direct path to your subconscious to resolve chronic pain, anxiety, and limiting patterns for those who have tried everything."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-base leading-tight mb-4">
        Unstuck for Good. A Direct Path to Your Subconscious to Resolve Chronic Pain, Anxiety, and Limiting Patterns.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        For those who have tried everything, this powerful, eyes-open method helps you communicate directly with your inner mind to reclaim complete control of your health and life.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-brand-primary text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors text-lg w-full sm:w-auto">
          Book a Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="border border-brand-primary text-brand-primary font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-brand-primary hover:text-white transition-colors text-lg w-full sm:w-auto">
          Learn About My Method
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-base mb-4">A Revolutionary Approach to Healing</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        My method treats the mind like a computer, allowing us to find the root of the issue and give it new, empowering instructions. The process is simple, direct, and unfolds in three clear steps.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 text-left">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-base mb-2">Step 1: Identify & Communicate</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            We establish a direct, eyes-open line of communication with your subconscious. Using simple physical responses, we pinpoint the exact root cause of your issue, tracing it back to when the problematic pattern began.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-base mb-2">Step 2: Review & Rescript</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            We guide you to key past memories where limiting beliefs were formed. Here, we neutralize their emotional charge by reframing the experience and "rescripting" the old negative messages into positive, empowering ones.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-base mb-2">Step 3: Install New Programming</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Finally, we replace the old patterns with new, clear instructions aligned with your goals. Through powerful visualization, we install an upgraded "mental software" that works for you, not against you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Client Success Stories Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-base mb-4">Real Change for Real People</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        These are the kinds of breakthroughs my clients experience.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-text-muted italic border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4 mb-4 flex-grow">
            "I felt like it was a whole body exfoliation, but for my soul. I feel lighter and more free... I truly feel as though you gave me back 15 years of my life."
          </blockquote>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-base">Amanda G.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">On Profound Life Transformation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-text-muted italic border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4 mb-4 flex-grow">
            "Can truthfully say I've never had any type of mental health session benefit me to that degree... I was able to do this whole thing in one little session. Boom."
          </blockquote>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-base">Jonathan L.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">On Rapid Mental Health Breakthroughs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-text-muted italic border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4 mb-4 flex-grow">
            "After a year and a half of a level 10 migraine, it was gone after one session... It has absolutely changed my life."
          </blockquote>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-base">Jolene R.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">On Resolving Chronic Neurological Pain</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-text-muted italic border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4 mb-4 flex-grow">
            "Thanks to Damian, I have not taken medication for migraines in at least a year... I have control over my own well being. Itâ€™s life changing."
          </blockquote>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-base">Jill S.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">On Ending Reliance on Medication</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

